DESCRIPTION
Encourage your rabbit’s natural foraging instincts with Full Cheeks Rabbit Forage Mix Salad. Made with love for rabbits, these treats are rich in fiber, and satisfy your small pet’s foraging instincts. We believe caring for your furry little one should be as easy as loving them, and now it can be. Our products are specially made for them, and are designed to be simple for you. All they need to do is what they do best: give lots of love. Only at PetSmart.
